{
  "stem": "24111.6",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And at the same time, Switzerland had a very German-friendly attitude and actually returned Jewish refugees on the border, taken on the border, directly into German hands.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, again, perhaps only hearsay.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But a wonderful film was made in Switzerland for their own people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The film name is And it's an old archives, and it tells the story of people returned into the hand of the Germans.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "To come back, we stayed three, four days.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The money went to Ponte Tresa, to the smugglers, into the hands of Chichibo.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this we know because Joschko received the notification, Chichibo came back to Nonantola and told him, now you bring-- now you can bring the children.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At the time, Joschko was perhaps 26, 27.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now our time-- we couldn't stay longer in the home of Dr.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Lichtheim.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had to go to the Swiss Fremdenpolizei and represent us, which we did.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And at first, they couldn't believe that we made it to Zurich, because we told them we came from Italy.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he said, how come you were not caught in Lugano, in the Italian part?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So after a while they interned us in one of the worst internation-- intern camps in the German part of Switzerland by the name of Busserach.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was near Solothurn and Basel.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Swiss police concerned with foreigners-- Fremdenpolizei.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's a special group of Swiss police under the Swiss government, of course.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now I have to come back to Chichibo.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Chichibo received the money after a few days' wait.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he decided to make it back to Joschko to bring the children.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And can you imagine?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He made their way back to Como Chiasso to Milano on those terrible train rides back.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
